{
  "uuid": "37a98dbf26a6a53caf5c0a43afcf4d0b",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales and Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<h3>Role Overview</h3><p>We are seeking a driven <strong>Sales & Marketing Executive</strong> to develop and manage the Vietnamese market for our services in <strong>immigration consultancy, education placement, company incorporation, and professional course sales</strong>.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><strong>Sales & Client Acquisition</strong></p><ul><li><p>Promote and sell immigration, education placement, company incorporation, and training courses to Vietnamese-speaking clients</p></li><li><p>Handle enquiries and conduct client consultations</p></li><li><p>Follow up on leads and close sales</p></li><li><p>Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets</p></li></ul><p><strong>Marketing & Market Development</strong></p><ul><li><p>Support marketing campaigns targeting the Vietnam market</p></li><li><p>Assist with Vietnamese-language marketing materials and client communication</p></li><li><p>Identify new business opportunities and referral partners</p></li></ul><p><strong>Client Relationship Management</strong></p><ul><li><p>Build and maintain long-term relationships with clients and partners</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams to ensure smooth service delivery</p></li></ul><p><strong>Reporting & Administration</strong></p><ul><li><p>Maintain accurate sales records and client documentation</p></li><li><p>Prepare basic sales and performance reports</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Prefer to have taken Higher Vietnamese (advanced Vietnamese language)</strong></p></li><li><p>Fluent in <strong>spoken and written Vietnamese</strong>, with strong grammar and professional writing ability</p></li><li><p>Good command of <strong>English</strong> (Mandarin is an advantage)</p></li><li><p>Diploma / Degree in Marketing, Business, or related field preferred</p></li><li><p>Minimum <strong>1–2 years of sales or marketing experience</strong> (education, immigration, or consultancy experience is a plus)</p></li><li><p>Target-driven, self-motivated, and results-oriented</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li></ul><h3>What We Offer</h3><ul><li><p>Competitive basic salary + commission</p></li><li><p>Structured training and product knowledge support</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunities in a growing consultancy firm</p></li><li><p>Performance-based incentives</p></li></ul>",
